Classes in edu.udel.bioinformatics.siterule that implement KingdomLine
 class KingdomLineImpl
          Author: Chuming Chen
University of Delaware
Center for Bioinformatics and Computational Biology
Date: July 12, 2013

The taxonomic classification is composed of the kingdom, optionally followed by the name of a sub-taxon, to further limit the application of the Site Rule to any taxonomic level.
